message.content:
To help summarize your investment strategy effectively, I need to understand a bit more about your financial goals and risk tolerance. Here are two questions to get us started:

1. What are your primary investment goals? (e.g., retirement, wealth accumulation, saving for a major purchase)
2. How would you describe your risk tolerance? (e.g., conservative, moderate, aggressive)

Your answers will help me provide a tailored summary of your investment strategy!
